<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center title"><span class="first-letter">W</span>HY <span class="first-letter">O</span>NORG</h2>
        <div class="row mt-3">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <img src="/images/index_about1.jpg" alt="About" width="100%" class="rounded">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4 text-muted"  style="font-size: 15px;">
                <div><span style="font-weight: 600;">Nowadays</span>, world is facing with the most dangerous pandemic disease covid-19. Therefore, somehow everything is done online, including education.</div>
                <div class="mt-2">Facilitating online education is just as important as through educational institutions. In this web application project, it is possible to create an institution virtually. As such, students and teachers can be part of that institution. This allows teachers to easily post lecture notes, previous year question papers and links of videos of lecture classes. Teachers posting notes in this way, allows students to access all these notes by joining under the respective teachers.</div>
                <div class="mt-2">In addition, the website provides instant access to information on all activities in the institution for all students and teachers.Teachers can publish the results of the examinations conducted in the respective classes. Students can know their internal marks too.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 text-muted" style="font-size: 15px;">
                <div class="mb-1" style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;">Main objectives of OnOrg are :</div>
                <ul class="text-muted">
                    <li>Head of the educational institution can easily pass important memos to all students and teachers.</li>
                    <li>Teachers can publish lecture notes, previous year question papers, links of videos of lecture classes etc. and students can access this very fastly.</li>
                    <li>Students can refer to classes from anywhere at anytime.</li>
                    <li> Head of the institution can schedule meeting with teachers.</li>
                    <li>Head of the institution can block students if they disobeyed the rules of institution.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center title"><span class="first-letter">A</span>DMINS & <span class="first-letter">U</span>SERS</h2>
        <div class="row mt-3">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <h4 style="font-weight: 600;;">Admins</h4>
                <div class="text-muted" style="font-size: 15px;">They are specialized programmers who create, manage and ensure the proper working of the web application. Here, they are entrusted with the task to create the web application for different types of users which are capable to interact in different levels. They have the central control over the datas and databases included in the web application. It is their duty to verify the user's genuineness.</div>
                <div class="text-muted mt-2" style="font-size: 15px;">Administrators has programmed the web application in such a way that institution, tutor and student can communicate. Administrators generate a secret code for institution account. This secret code has to be given to tutors and students to join under that institution. Hence, we can prevent fake users.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <img src="/images/index_about2.jpg" alt="Administrator" width="100%" class="rounded">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
