                <img src="/images/index_about3.jpg" alt="Users" width="100%" class="rounded">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <h4 style="font-weight: 600;">Users</h4>
                <div class="text-muted" style="font-size: 15px;">They are any individual who is using services and not involved with supporting or developing a computer or service. Users can create their own accounts using their confidential informations and can also use their facilities. Users can create different accounts by using the same informations for different roles. By using this feature an authorized user can invite another user under his/her specified sector.</div>
                <div class="text-muted mt-2" style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;">Users of this web application can be basically classified into three namely : </div>
                <ul class="text-muted mt-1" style="font-size: 15px;">
                    <li>Head of the educational institution</li>
                    <li>Tutor</li>
                    <li>Student</li>
                </ul>
