</section>

<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center title"><span class="first-letter">O</span>PERATIONS & <span class="first-letter">F</span>UNCTIONS</h2>
        <div class="row mt-3">
            <div class="col-12 mb-2">
                <div class="text-muted" style="font-size: 15px;">The operations and functions for each user can be described as modules.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="text-muted mb-1" style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;">Facilities for Institution :</div>
                <ul class="text-muted" style="font-size: 15px;">
                    <li>Sign up using email id and a secret code is automatically generated.</li>
                    <li>Can provide notifications for teachers and students of various activities.</li>
                    <li>Institution can access datas of students fastly whennecessary.</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="text-muted mt-2 mb-1" style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;">Facilities for Tutor :</div>
                <ul class="text-muted" style="font-size: 15px;">
                    <li>Sign up using email id and secret code of institution.</li>
                    <li>Tutors can post lecture notes and other study materials from anywhere at any time.</li>
                    <li>Tutors can upload marks of students.</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="text-muted mt-2 mb-1" style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;">Facilities for Student :</div>
                <ul class="text-muted" style="font-size: 15px;">
                    <li>Sign up using email id and secret code of institution.</li>
                    <li>Can access to lecture notes and study materials from anywhere at any time.</li>
                    <li>Students can get their results of examinations.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <img src="/images/index_about4.jpg" alt="Operations and Functions" width="100%" class="rounded">
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 text-muted mb-4">
                <div style="font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700;">Basic Working Strategy</div>
                <div class="mt-2" style="font-size: 15px;">The basic workingstrategy of this dynamic website is very simple. It can be explained as a step-by-step process.</div>
                <div class="mt-1" style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Step 1 :</span> Head of the institution have to create anaccount.</div>
                <div class="mt-1" style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Step 2 :</span> Students and tutors have to join under theinstitution using the secret code. </div>
                <div class="mt-1" style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Step 3 :</span> Tutors have to create classrooms for eachsubjects. They can post lecture notes and other study materials.</div>
                <div class="mt-1" style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Step 4 :</span> Students have to join the virtual classroomsusing link or classroom code. Thus, they can access to the notes providedby tutors.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

